items.badge_description: At a new place and don't want to choose a pint of something you may not like? Grab a few tasters! Enjoy some small pours and then decide which to upgrade to a full pour. That's 145 checkins with the serving style of Taster. Try 5 more for Level 30!

Porters and Stouts are rich with both history and flavor. Roasty, dark, and delicious, these two styles helped start it all. That’s 60 different beers with the style of Porter or Stout. Try 5 more to unlock Level 13.

Wouldn’t it be nice if milk stouts came directly from beer producing cows? While this unfortunately isn’t the case (yet) they do have a full body and sweetness due to a larger amount of lactose and sugars. That's 15 different beers with the style of Milk / Sweet Stout. Try 5 more for Level 4!

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 50 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%. Try 5 more for Level 11!

items.checkin_comment: That's good, some sweet to cancel the bitter. A little chocolate but not overloaded. Solid.
